creator: Telldus Technologies AB
descriptionHtml:
Telldus Flow: The official app for the Telldus Flow! system.

Control and monitor your home, office or summer cottage from anywhere with our easy to use, modern and fast application.
descriptionShort: Automate your home with Telldus TellStick

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
To enhance the experience of our Smartline Flow users, and open up the possibilities to work with the home automation devices in Telldus, we have combined Smartline Flow and Telldus offerings into a fresh new app of Telldus Flow.

Our fully revamped Telldus Flow's interface offers:
Easier device onboarding
Control Smartline devices remotely
Simple to use services to quickly automate your home

Smartline Flow devices are supported now. Telldus devices will be supported in later releases.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Welcome to the new and revamped Telldus Flow App. This version enables you to :
1: Manage Bluetooth devices locally
2: Remotely manage Bluetooth devices with the new Tellstick flow gateway
3: Migrate old Smartline Flow app devices into this app seamlessly
4: Automate your Bluetooth devices with pre-built automation cards

Known behaviour :
Restart Smartline app once for smooth migration.

descriptionShort: Automate your home with Telldus TellStick

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Introducing the new Telldus Flow app
Simplified login process using one-time passwords* (OTP)
Control locally all your Smartline Flow devices without any hub or gateway
Control both Smartline Flow** & your existing 433/Z-wave devices remotely
Easy to use Automation cards for home-automation
Set up monitor for all your gateways
Smartline Flow app users can easily migrate using the Migration function in the Smartline Flow app.
* Additional SMS charges may apply.
** A TellStick Flow is required
